[ ] Lazy-stamp workspace_id on write when a workspace lacks one $init already mints on init.rs:103; add the missing lazy path on mutating commands: mint now_v7 and persist to config.json$ !1 #019f6ea6-737b-7f83-91bb-bd8143ca9e9e
[ ] Read path uses transient graph id when workspace_id is absent $fixes un-initd workspace dropping all query rows; fall back to TRANSIENT_GRAPH_URI, never persist from the read side$ !1 #019f6ea6-aa3b-7fb3-bfe3-02e132bd46a7
[ ] Guarantee action UUID write-back before any id becomes durable $parser.rs:331 mints now_v7 per-read; the ephemeral id must never escape into a persisted < ref, sidecar entry, serialized graph edge, or archived file$ !1 #019f6ea6-aa4d-74b2-a071-5313536bd78e
[ ] Flag actions without a persisted id and steer to normalize $doctor/lint: identity is unstable until the id is written to the line$ !2 #019f6ea6-aa5a-7332-910c-ac9effe0c72e
[ ] Promote resolved name-refs in \< deps to UUIDs on write $parser.rs:313 leaves resolved_uuid None for name refs; persist the durable uuid so the ref survives moves and archival$ !2 #019f6ea6-aa67-79d0-9738-7677fb30c2c4
